basic steps
1.creating a folder
2.creating a package.json file
3.install express
4.creating index.js file
5.import express inside the index.js
6.create an app using the express
7.setup port number
8.resolving http request 
9.HTTP response code
      1xx - Informaation
      2xx - Success
      3xx - Redirection
      4xx - client error
      5xx - Server error
10.jwt(JSON web token) token-for authenthication
sign()

11.middleware
   1.application specific middleware-for entire application
   2.router specific middleware- token validation -verify()

12.databse integration
install mongoose
db connect via mongoose
create model using mongoose
13.asynchronous function resolving
  resolve-.then()
  reject - catch()

14 CORS- cross origin resourse sharing
   install cors
